ht=\"400\" font-family=\"Inter,sans-serif\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">$578 vs $600 budget. Consistency here saved</text><text x=\"32\" y=\"366\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#6B6258\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Inter,sans-serif\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">you $264 over 6 months.</text><text x=\"354\" y=\"328\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#4A7C59\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Inter,sans-serif\" text-anchor=\"end\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"0.6\">↗</text><rect x=\"16\" y=\"432\" width=\"358\" height=\"140\" rx=\"14\" fill=\"#FFFFFF\" opacity=\"1\" stroke=\"#E4DED6\" stroke-width=\"1\"/><rect x=\"32\" y=\"450\" width=\"37\" height=\"20\" rx=\"10\" fill=\"#7B9FD4\" opacity=\"0.15\" stroke=\"none\" stroke-width=\"0\"/><text x=\"50.5\" y=\"464\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#7B9FD4\" font-weight=\"700\" font-family=\"Inter,sans-serif\" text-anchor=\"middle\" letter-spacing=\"0.5\" opacity=\"1\">TIP</text><text x=\"32\" y=\"486\" font-size=\"16\" fill=\"#1C1814\" font-weight=\"700\" font-family=\"Inter,sans-serif\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">Cancel unused subscriptions</text><text x=\"32\" y=\"508\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#6B6258\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Inter,sans-serif\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">3 subscriptions haven't been used in 60+</text><text x=\"32\" y=\"524\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#6B6258\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Inter,sans-serif\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">days, totalling $43/month.</text><text x=\"354\" y=\"486\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#7B9FD4\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Inter,sans-serif\" text-anchor=\"end\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"0.6\">↗</text><rect x=\"16\" y=\"590\" width=\"358\" height=\"140\" rx=\"14\" fill=\"#FFFFFF\" opacity=\"1\" stroke=\"#E4DED6\" stroke-width=\"1\"/><rect x=\"32\" y=\"608\" width=\"72\" height=\"20\" rx=\"10\" fill=\"#B07FC5\" opacity=\"0